title: Ep. 9 - Thanksgiving
itunes:title: Ep. 9 - Thanksgiving
description:
It’s someone’s favorite holiday but we won’t tell you who. (Hint: Her name rhymes with Fendi…)

Our host gets the warm and fuzzies because she doesn’t let a dropped turkey or a burned casserole throw her off her game. Let it be what it is and raise a glass to celebrate all the good things in your life.
